This project represents original work in the field of LLM-API integration,
specifically the concept and implementation of "Universal Code Mode" for
reducing token usage across multiple API types.

Key Innovations:
- Universal adapter pattern for multi-source API integration
- .agent-ready.json agent discovery mechanism
- 98% token reduction through generated code exploration
- Type-safe wrapper generation for MCP, OpenAPI, and future sources

Original repository: https://github.com/tyranosurasmax/MCP-CODEGEN
First commit: November 2025

